    <h2>List of Things you'll love in Kano</h2>
    <ol>
      <li>Kano is beautiful</li>
      <li>Kano booms with business. There is always a profitable business for you</li>
      <li>Nunu, Fura, Kunu Haya, Gurasa, Suya, Balango and everything in between</li>
      <li>Kano has a Rich History</li>
    </ol>
<h2>List of Annoying things in Kano </h2>
    <body>
<ul>
  <li>You can't thrive without Hausa Language</li>
  <li>There are mosquitoes everywhere</li>
  <li>They don't take schooling/education seriously</li>
  <li>Most women sit in their homes idle when they should be empowered</li>
  <li>Kano people are not blessed with culinary skills</li>
</ul>


